## OS families

Each platform is assigned to a group of non-overlpaping families:

<!-- platform-hierarchy-start -->

```mermaid
---
config: {"mindmap": {"padding": 5}}
---
mindmap
    ((Extra Platforms))
        )≛ UNIX_LAYERS(
            (Ͼ cygwin)
        )Ⅴ SYSTEM_V(
            (➿ aix)
            (🌞 solaris)
        )⊎ OTHER_UNIX(
            (🐃 hurd)
        )≚ LINUX_LAYERS(
            (⊞ wsl1)
            (⊞ wsl2)
        )🐧 LINUX(
            (🐧 altlinux)
            (🙂 amzn)
            (🤖 android)
            (🎗️ arch)
            (⛑️ buildroot)
            (💠 centos)
            (꩜ cloudlinux)
            (🌀 debian)
            (🐽 exherbo)
            (🎩 fedora)
            (🗜️ gentoo)
            (🐃 guix)
            (🤹 ibm_powerkvm)
            (🤹 kvmibm)
            (🌿 linuxmint)
            (⍥ mageia)
            (💫 mandriva)
            ( nobara)
            (🦎 opensuse)
